{
  "module": "CAP-LOGISTICS-PILOT",
  "file": "backend/openapi/openapi.yaml",
  "why": "openapi.yaml omits the request bodies of five logistics operations (backend rejects a body-less call with 422/415) and declares no 2xx response schemas for any of the nine. The generated TS client therefore types requestBody?: never for those five and data as untyped for all nine; web/src/console/logistics/logisticsApi.ts works around this with `as never` body casts and hand-written response interfaces. Applying this patch and regenerating clients/{ts,kotlin,swift} removes both workarounds.",
  "datetimeDivergence": {
    "finding": "The deployed rest crate deserializes ReleaseBody.due_at, PodBody.confirmed_at, and SettleBody.settled_at as plain time::OffsetDateTime WITHOUT #[serde(with = \"time::serde::rfc3339\")], deviating from the repo convention and from openapi.yaml's declared `dueAt: format: date-time`. With the workspace time 0.3.47 feature set (serde, serde-well-known; serde-human-readable NOT unified into the build), the only accepted wire form is time's default serde tuple [year, ordinalDay, hour, minute, second, nanosecond, offsetH, offsetM, offsetS]; an RFC3339 string is rejected with 422. Empirically verified against time 0.3.47; the backend's own story test (backend/app/tests/logistics_pilot_story.rs) only passes because serde_json::json! serializes OffsetDateTime to that tuple.",
    "backendFix": "Add #[serde(with = \"time::serde::rfc3339\")] to due_at (ReleaseBody), confirmed_at (PodBody), and settled_at (SettleBody) in backend/crates/logistics/rest/src/lib.rs so the implementation matches the declared date-time contract. The tuple form keeps parsing under time's lenient visitor, so the frontend's interim encoding does not break during rollout.",
    "frontendToday": "web/src/console/logistics/logisticsApi.ts encodes the three fields with toTimeWire() (UTC tuple) so release/pod/settle work against the deployed backend; drop toTimeWire and pass ISO strings once the backendFix lands.",
    "caution": "Do NOT apply the format: date-time declarations for confirmedAt/settledAt below as documentation of current behavior — they describe the POST-backendFix contract. Applying the spec patch without the backend annotation codifies a format the server rejects."
  },
  "afterApply": "regenerate committed clients (openapi_drift Rust test + check:api-drift:portable/swift CI gates); then web/src/console/logistics/logisticsApi.ts can drop its five `as never` casts and replace its response interfaces with components[\"schemas\"] aliases",
  "requestBodies": [
    {
      "operationId": "pickLogisticsFulfillment",
      "path": "/api/v1/logistics/fulfillments/{fulfillment_id}/pick",
      "add": {
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": false,
                "required": [
                  "branchId",
                  "pickedQuantity"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "branchId": {
                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
                  },
                  "pickedQuantity": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "format": "int64",
                    "minimum": 0
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "operationId": "packLogisticsFulfillment",
      "path": "/api/v1/logistics/fulfillments/{fulfillment_id}/pack",
      "add": {
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": false,
                "required": [
                  "branchId"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "branchId": {
                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "operationId": "dispatchLogisticsShipment",
      "path": "/api/v1/logistics/fulfillments/{fulfillment_id}/dispatch",
      "add": {
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": false,
                "required": [
                  "branchId",
                  "carrierName",
                  "vehicleReference"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "branchId": {
                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
                  },
                  "carrierName": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "maxLength": 120
                  },
                  "vehicleReference": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "maxLength": 120
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "operationId": "verifyLogisticsPod",
      "path": "/api/v1/logistics/shipments/{shipment_id}/pod",
      "add": {
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": false,
                "required": [
                  "branchId",
                  "recipientName",
                  "evidenceReference",
                  "confirmedAt"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "branchId": {
                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
                  },
                  "recipientName": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "maxLength": 160
                  },
                  "evidenceReference": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "pattern": "^evidence://"
                  },
                  "confirmedAt": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "date-time"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "operationId": "settleLogisticsOperationalCost",
      "path": "/api/v1/logistics/shipments/{shipment_id}/settlements",
      "add": {
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "additionalProperties": false,
                "required": [
                  "branchId",
                  "currencyCode",
                  "amountMinor",
                  "settledAt"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "branchId": {
                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
                  },
                  "currencyCode": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "enum": [
                      "KRW"
                    ]
                  },
                  "amountMinor": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "format": "int64",
                    "minimum": 0
                  },
                  "settledAt": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "date-time"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "responseSchemas": {
    "note": "add typed 2xx application/json content to each operation, mirroring backend/crates/logistics/adapter-postgres/src/lib.rs json! outputs verbatim",
    "createLogisticsAsn": {
      "201": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status",
          "branchId"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "EXPECTED"
            ]
          },
          "branchId": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "receiveLogisticsAsn": {
      "200": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "PARTIAL_RECEIVED",
              "RECEIVED"
            ]
          },
          "receivedQuantity": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "cumulative received total; absent on an idempotent replay"
          },
          "replayed": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "present and true only on an idempotent replay"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "putawayLogisticsAsn": {
      "200": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "PUTAWAY"
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "releaseLogisticsFulfillment": {
      "201": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status",
          "reservedQuantity"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "RELEASED"
            ]
          },
          "reservedQuantity": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "pickLogisticsFulfillment": {
      "200": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status",
          "pickedQuantity"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "PICKED",
              "SHORT_PICK"
            ]
          },
          "pickedQuantity": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "packLogisticsFulfillment": {
      "200": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status",
          "pickedQuantity"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "PACKED"
            ]
          },
          "pickedQuantity": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "dispatchLogisticsShipment": {
      "201": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "fulfillmentId",
          "status"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid",
            "description": "created shipment id"
          },
          "fulfillmentId": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "DISPATCHED"
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "verifyLogisticsPod": {
      "200": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status",
          "recipientConfirmedEvidenceReference",
          "slaAssessment"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "DELIVERED"
            ]
          },
          "recipientConfirmedEvidenceReference": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "slaAssessment": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "MET",
              "BREACHED"
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "settleLogisticsOperationalCost": {
      "200": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "status",
          "operationalCost",
          "financeGlPosting"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Uuid"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "SETTLED"
            ]
          },
          "operationalCost": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": [
              "currency",
              "amountMinor"
            ],
            "properties": {
              "currency": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "KRW"
                ]
              },
              "amountMinor": {
                "type": "integer",
                "format": "int64"
              }
            }
          },
          "financeGlPosting": {
            "type": "null",
            "description": "always null by design — no GL/finance edge in the pilot"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
